{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_13_01",
  "title": "白石千紗 1話 ラヴラビに関われるなんて",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――とある休日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ。面白かったですね、映画\nお姉ちゃんの演技も凄かったです……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.8333333532
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "試写会には予定が合わなくて行けなかったから\nちゃんと観れて良かった～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.8999993205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと楽しみにしていたもんな\nプレミアシートのチケットまで用意して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんが主演の映画ですから\n一番の特等席で観たかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.6999995748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "それに、次に観る映画も決まっちゃいました！\n上映前の予告で、あの名作が4Kで蘇るって……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.0666664957
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "映画の前の予告……あぁ、ラヴズ・ラビリンスか\n確か、昔の名作ホラー映画だったよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.5000020345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ラヴラビは童話を元にしたホラー映画で\nとにかく心理描写が秀逸でつい引き込まれちゃうんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "監督のクラフモさんが撮る映画は独特な世界観が\nとっても魅力的で、賞も沢山受賞してるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.6000020345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "それが4Kになるのはとっても――ってごめんなさい！\n大好きなホラー映画の話だから、つい熱くなっちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.5333372314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗がその映画を凄く好きだって分かったから\nむしろ聞けて良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それに、ちょうど俺もその映画の話を\nしようとしていたところなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.7666646321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　もしかして、予告を見てラヴラビのことが\n気になったとか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.8999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それもあるけど、今回は仕事の話だな\n千紗に遊園地から仕事のオファーが来ているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4666625977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.6999977946
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "今度、ラヴラビが復活するタイミングに合わせて\n日本の遊園地とコラボすることになったらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "作品の世界観が体験出来るお化け屋敷を作るから\nその公式アンバサダーになってほしいとのことだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.0333389282
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "私がラヴラビの案件に関われるんですか！？\n嬉しいですけど、どうして……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.7333372314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は過去にお化け屋敷のプロデュースを\nしたことがあるだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それに、クラフモ監督のファンだってことを\n先方が知ってくれていてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.8000028808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "千紗さえ良ければぜひ、アンバサダーと監修協力を\nお願いしたい、との連絡が来ているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.0391601388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.0333445231
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことなら、ぜひ引き受けたいです！\nこんな機会、もう二度とないかも……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.5666807372
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "ラヴラビの世界観を再現するなら\nやっぱり童話のモチーフは外せないよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "メルヘンとホラーの奇跡的なバランスを再現するには\nアレとアレを……あ、深海生物の要素も忘れずに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.9666695475
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それだけやる気があれば、先方も喜びそうだ\nじゃあ、引き受ける方向で話を進めておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.5666625976
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_01-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\nラヴラビに関われるなんて、本当に楽しみです……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_mouse-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9966.66666660002,
          "startTime": 179.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.8999908447
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.8999908447
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
